HEADWORD: Nemophilist
<hw>Ne*moph"i*list</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Nemophily</er>.]</ety> <def>One who is fond of forest or forest
scenery; a haunter of the woods.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

